{"tid":1632251,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"警察酷刑完大部份人唔係骨折就昏迷，點解神獸出完黎個人仲行得走得？","createTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:43:20.000Z","uid":156394,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d5d6f7961faf76d63e68a7ecd3691b03293f77a5","tid":1632251,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:02.000Z","msg":"第一件事<br />\n拉撚走晒d和理非同左膠<br />\n<br />\n第二件事<br />\n雨傘陣，擋視野<br />\n<br />\n第三件事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當一個法律制度同執法者保障唔到公義同市民安全，所有人都係可以合法自衛。<br />\n<br />\n仲有，即使真係咁唔好彩，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3c82d3264969d85c155aecd1adb112b6f08aebef","tid":1632251,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c83d1fc77ec80479af7e26231a73983e9521736","tid":1632251,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:06.000Z","msg":"幫手推下啊，唔該大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9beed6a5a8146a49da3634f1b92c2304469ee336","tid":1632251,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"因為神獸撞親都係頭睇落好傷？"},{"pid":"247e10676fe24f74c69aeaafbbaca514bacab386","tid":1632251,"uid":156394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9beed6a5a8146a49da3634f1b92c2304469ee336","tid":1632251,"uid":9412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:06.000Z","msg":"因為神獸撞親都係頭睇落好傷？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"個畫面唔好睇，但不完美，可接受，需改善。"},{"pid":"9da5ac831f9280ff1c38df5ede55b62e843a307b","tid":1632251,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:55.000Z","msg":"推啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大力d同去推"},{"pid":"c9e456c87b1999751ddac15cdc157eeeb4c6a4c7","tid":1632251,"uid":142010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:31.000Z","msg":"對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修<br />\n<br />\n1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX<br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.MEMO紙<br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.善用1823<br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.蟲系魔法師<br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):<br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚<br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢飛個靚髮或者化下妝就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命<br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"91e362320065354e4cfa335426c4fa43aecea802","tid":1632251,"uid":91736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:50.000Z","msg":"FUCK CHINAZI"},{"pid":"a8b3fd8cd2ec1ef931b9f43a8a7eb7f4f631fb85","tid":1632251,"uid":156394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:26.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 